{"tid":2273621,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"李克強河南視察民情 高處突傳淒厲喊聲「冤枉啊」","createTime":"2020-11-06T01:14:48.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-06T01:18:51.000Z","uid":184679,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"80fc8f68f5adf0d7d2860398ec7b87212ce7ac4c","tid":2273621,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T01:14:49.000Z","msg":"中國國務院總理李克強近來頻繁公開活動，11月初到河南安陽、鄭州考察，他在安陽一處社區考察時，遇到民眾在高空大喊「冤枉」，讓在旁的官員非常尷尬。<br />\n<br />\n《新華網》報導，李克強11月3日至4日到河南安陽、鄭州考察冬季小麥的生長、農民收入、生活等情況，並到食品公司了解生產經營情況。李克強也到社區查看民眾居住情況，稱加強保障房屋建設是推動新型城鎮化的重要任務，建設、租售模式都可以因地制宜積極探索。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3343598\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3343598&d=RNNv2si1j6MvuJ657i5J8pLurRSHZiEGX9rhKonVocs%3D&h=f0e45bf6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3343598&h=fd19ad3d\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3343598</a>"},{"pid":"dbc0bfd2838e1d4c680d3d0259686714bc3c28d8","tid":2273621,"uid":151074,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T01:16:10.000Z","msg":"国安點做嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b34fcff1135263cc5c2fd4de3413bdd3056b05d6","tid":2273621,"uid":235250,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T01:18:51.000Z","msg":"仆街，睇錯李克強自己叫冤枉"}]}